 pressure, cholesterol, and blood sugar levels.</p><p class=\"h_hatch-element--p h_hatch-element--body-1 h_markdown__p\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 1em 0px 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><div class=\"ez_container ez_container--break ez_container--wide\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; padding-right: 80px; padding-left: 80px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1184px; margin-top: 16px;\"><div class=\"ez_block ez_break\" data-analytics-section=\"BREAK_8\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><hr class=\"ez_break__dots\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; border-top: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-image: url(&quot;https://dodmzloxz80g8.cloudfront.net/hatch/assets/circles_divider-9981f0a6ce4e68b5fd876a1c70843d3fce33d587dc4d76bcb987da3879d9a8bf.svg&quot;); height: 20px; background-position: center center; margin: 0px;\"></div></div><div class=\"ez_container ez_container--markdown ez_container--inset\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; padding-right: 80px; padding-left: 80px; width: 986.656px; max-width: 986.667px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 16px;\"><div class=\"ez_block ez_markdown\" data-analytics-section=\"SECTION_9\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><div class=\"h_markdown\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; word-break: break-word;\"><p class=\"h_hatch-element--p h_hatch-element--body-1 h_markdown__p\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 1em 0px 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\">Whether you’re looking to rekindle a mind-body connection, or need to stretch it out after a multi-day streaming marathon, make yoga your place to return.</p><p class=\"h_hatch-element--p h_hatch-element--body-1 h_markdown__p\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; margin: 1em 0px 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: 0px;\">No matter where you are or what’s happening in the world, Manduka invites you to #PracticeOn.</p></div></div></div></section>', NULL, '2020-06-03 21:43:03');
