(2, 'Post-Pandemic, the Fashion Industry Will Rely on Freelancers More Than Ever', 'post-pandemic-the-fashion-industry-will-rely-on-freelancers-more-than-ever', 'post-pandemic-the-fashion-industry-will-rely-on-freelancers-more-than-ever.jpg', 'As lockdowns lift, brands are likely to hire temporary employees that require less investment. What does that mean for freelancers’ labour rights?', '<header class=\"entry-header\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Lato, serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h1 class=\"entry-title\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 17px; font-family: Montserrat, serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 27.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3.4px;\">A NOTE FROM ME // ORGANIZATIONS &amp; BRANDS TO SUPPORT</h1><div class=\"entry-meta\" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.the-atlantic-pacific.com/category/edit/\" style=\"color: rgb(3, 3, 3);\">EDIT &amp; ETC.</a>&nbsp;//&nbsp;<date>JUNE 1, 2020</date></div></header><div class=\"entry-content\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Lato, serif; font-size: 15px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\">I have been donating, signing petitions, and calling to help bring awareness, change, and justice to the racial inequalities that exist in our country. I am committed to being a better ally and am in the process of examining truly what that means and what that will look like going forward.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\">I am making a commitment to donate money immediately, and I’m also setting up recurring donations to organizations that support/uplift the Black community. I’m making a commitment to shop and support more Black owned businesses, and follow and engage with more Black creators on social media channels. I will be holding the brands that I work with accountable to ensure that all campaigns and events that I am fortunate to be a part of are diverse and inclusive. This is what you’ll see on my site and social media channels, but also know that I will be working towards a more fair and just world in my everyday life by actively being anti-racist.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\">Below I am listing some important organizations that need support as well as highlighting a few of my favorite independent retailers and brands that are Black owned and operated.&nbsp;<em>As someone who spends I was encouraged to share how I can effect change with my wallet (and encourage others to spend)</em>. If you have additional ideas or would like to mention more organizations, retailers, or brands, please leave a comment for me. This list is not comprehensive…it is just a start.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">ORGANIZATIONS TO SUPPORT:</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\">When researching how to get involved and donate, I was looking for trusted, credible organizations that not only provide support, but create opportunities, and/or seek justice for those who are effected by systemic racism.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://www.naacp.org/about-us/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">NAACP</a>&nbsp;</span>// Their mission: The mission of the National Association for the Advancement of Colored People (NAACP) is to secure the political, educational, social, and economic equality of rights in order to eliminate race-based discrimination and ensure the health and well-being of all persons. I have set up a recurring donation to the NAACP, you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://secure.actblue.com/donate/naacp-1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"http://nbjc.org/about\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">The National Black Justice Coalition</a></span>&nbsp;// Their mission: The National Black Justice Coalition (NBJC) is a civil rights organization dedicated to the empowerment of Black lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, queer and same gender loving (LGBTQ/SGL) people, including people living with HIV/AIDS. NBJC’s mission is to end racism, homophobia, and LGBTQ/SGL bias and stigma. I have donated and you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mightycause.com/organization/nbjc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackgirlscode.com/what-we-do.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Black Girls Code</a></span>&nbsp;// Their mission: Black Girls CODE is devoted to showing the world that black girls can code, and do so much more. By reaching out to communities through workshops and after school programs, Black Girls CODE introduces computer coding lessons to young girls from underrepresented communities in programming languages such as Scratch or Ruby on Rails. Black Girls CODE has set out to prove to the world that girls of every color have the skills to become the programmers of tomorrow. I have donated and you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.blackgirlscode.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://100blackmen.org/who-we-are/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">100 Black Men of America</a></span>&nbsp;// Their organization: The 100 Black Men of America, Inc. is recognized as the nation’s top African American led mentoring organization. I have donated and you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://100blackmen.org/donate/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://www.innocenceproject.org/about/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">The Innocence Project</a>&nbsp;</span>// Their mission: The Innocence Project’s mission is to free the staggering number of innocent people who remain incarcerated, and to bring reform to the systems responsible for their unjust imprisonment. I have donated and you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.innocenceproject.org/donate/?f_src=FY20_web_x_gen_nmat_campGet000Involved_getinvolved\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://www.blackvisionsmn.org/about\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Black Vision Collective</a></span>&nbsp;// Their mission: Since 2017, Black Visions Collective, has been putting into practice the lessons learned from organizations before us in order to shape a political home for Black people across Minnesota. I have donated and you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://secure.everyaction.com/4omQDAR0oUiUagTu0EG-Ig2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://www.aclu.org/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline;\">ACLU</a></span>&nbsp;// Their mission: The American Civil Liberties Union (ACLU) exists to preserve and protect the liberties and privileges guaranteed to each individual by the Bill of Rights. These liberties include freedom of speech and expression, equal protection under the law, due process of law, and the right to personal privacy. I have set up a recurring donation to the ACLU, you can donate&nbsp;<a href=\"https://action.aclu.org/give/fund-every-fight-ahead?cid=7014A000001Zs9uQAC&amp;initms_aff=nat&amp;initms_chan=sem&amp;utm_medium=sem&amp;initms=200114_evergreenun_sem-402136071571-82611000622-aclu%20mission%20statement-p_segmentc_ggl&amp;utm_source=ggl&amp;utm_campaign=evergreenun&amp;utm_content=200114_sem-402136071571-82611000622-aclu%20mission%20statement-p_segmentc&amp;ms_aff=nat&amp;ms_chan=sem&amp;ms=200114_evergreenun_sem-402136071571-82611000622-aclu%20mission%20statement-p_segmentc_ggl&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwztL2BRATEiwAvnALcgbyCiBBBVQ0YySEYu_0Y8O-o4Nw_KhNZuvgvkZzdvcDhnfQrfP55xoCUx8QAvD_BwE&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwztL2BRATEiwAvnALcgbyCiBBBVQ0YySEYu_0Y8O-o4Nw_KhNZuvgvkZzdvcDhnfQrfP55xoCUx8QAvD_BwE\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(79, 98, 145); text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: 700;\">here</a>.</p><hr style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">RETAILERS AND BRANDS TO SUPPORT:</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8;\">I will dedicate more of my dollars spent as well as links/highlights to Black owned shops and designers. This is by no means an exhaustive list below, but just a small place to start and be inspired. I will continue to share.</p></div>', NULL, '2020-06-23 17:47:05'),
(3, 'Kendall Jenner suggests dressing up in all types of denim', 'kendall-jenner-suggests-dressing-up-in-all-types-of-denim', 'kendall-jenner-suggests-dressing-up-in-all-types-of-denim.jpg', 'From classic fashion inspiration to the modern streetwear mark, Kendall Jenner shows the ingenious transformation of a new generation \"denim icon\".', '<h2 style=\"margin: 1.75em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Time New Roman&quot;, Georgia, serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">As one of the most popular IT-girls of the decade, Kendall Jenner is considered a new fashion icon and an inspiration to wear beautiful clothes of many young people. Attached to her fashion style is a variety of denim outfits with a variety of formula combinations. So what are the \"tricks\" to help Kendall conquer this classic material?</span><br></h2><h2 style=\"margin: 1.75em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Time New Roman&quot;, Georgia, serif;\">RETRO FASHION BOILER</h2><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">In an interview, Kendall Jenner once shared that her inspiration for jeans originated from classic fashion icons such as Diana Prince or actress Jane Birkin. Therefore, this IT-girl has many times come down the street with jeans and a classic T-shirt or sweatshirt. Occasionally, she would add a simple blazer jacket outside.</p><div id=\"attachment_402233\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402233\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402233\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-mac-quan-jeans-ong-dung-va-so-mi-trang-phom-rong-Getty-Images.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner mặc quần jeans và sơ mi trắng rộng\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2999\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402233\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\">(Ảnh: Getty Images)</p></div><div id=\"attachment_402234\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402234\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402234\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-dien-quan-jeans-rach-ong-loe-Getty-Images.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner diện quần jeans rách, áo thun xanh dương và blazer màu kem\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"></div><div id=\"attachment_402234\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center;\"><div id=\"attachment_402234\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif\">Breaking point of the outfit is in the style of jeans bears flared personality. (Image: Getty Images)</font></div><div id=\"attachment_402234\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif\"><br></font></div><div id=\"attachment_402234\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif\">To make the outfit not too boring, Kendall will create accents with accessories, be it sunglasses, bags or shoes. When wearing a T-shirt, she also often \"changes the wind\" with striking shirt colors, helping to brighten the look but still keep the minimalist beauty.</font></div><p id=\"caption-attachment-402234\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\"><br></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-402234\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402235\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402235\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-mac-quan-denim-ong-lung-va-ao-thun-vang-Getty-Images.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner mặc áo thun vàng và quần jeans\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"></p></div><div id=\"attachment_402235\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402235\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\">(Ảnh: Getty Images)</p></div><h2 style=\"margin: 1.75em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Time New Roman&quot;, Georgia, serif;\">RELEASING WITH AROUND CROPTOP</h2><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Beautiful designs, beautiful designs, beautiful designs, beautiful designs, beautiful designs. Creativity in the clothes up to the beauty, she</p><div id=\"attachment_402236\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 2010px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402236\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402236\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-mac-quan-jeans-ong-dung-va-croptop-hai-day-mau-hong-Getty-Images.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner mặc áo hai dây lông vũ và quần jeans ống đứng\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402236\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\">Feminine feather-strapped dresses, which should be \"paired\" with a slender skirt, are \"personalized\" by Kendall with stand-up jeans. (Image: Getty Images)</p></div><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Kendall also often chooses a layer combination with a wide-fitting blazer or a bold, thin chiffon blouse. The slender necklace was an indispensable accessory for her when choosing this outfit. Taking advantage of the height and physique, she is comfortable wearing the waistband type of boyfriend pants that are quite picky about people wearing.</p><div id=\"attachment_402237\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 1610px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402237\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402237\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-mac-quan-jeans-ao-croptop-trang-blazer-ke-o-BACKGRID.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner mặc croptop trắng, quần jeans laggy và blazer\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2259\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402237\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\">(Ảnh: BACKGRID)</p></div><div id=\"attachment_402238\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 1290px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402238\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402238\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-dien-bralette-den-ao-voan-mong-va-quan-jeans-boyfriend-CelebMafia.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner mặc quần jeans boyfriends và áo bralette đen\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1920\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402238\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\">(Ảnh: CelebMafia)</p></div><h2 style=\"margin: 1.75em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Time New Roman&quot;, Georgia, serif;\">RELIGION DENIM FOOD</h2><p style=\"\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif\">As a follower of denim, Kendall Jenner owns almost all the hottest jeans today. The 24-year-old model favors comfortable designs like classic baggy and mom jeans. Besides, the stylish bootcut flared pants also often accompany her down the street. Kendall\'s coordination is also not picky, in contrast, very easy to refer and apply in everyday fashion.</font><br></p><div id=\"attachment_402239\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 1290px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402239\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402239\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402221/Kendall-Jenner-mac-quan-jeans-va-ao-thun-trang-Getty-Images.jpg\" alt=\"Kendall Jenner diện áo thu