(4, 'Skirts spread - Bao cuoi cherish feminine beauty', 'skirts-spread-bao-cuoi-cherish-feminine-beauty', 'skirts-spread-bao-cuoi-cherish-feminine-beauty.jpg', 'For girls pursuing a retro style with romantic touches, skirts with floral motifs and puffy sleeves are a must-see mix.', '<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Besides wrap dress and pencil skirt, spread skirt is one of the indispensable items of girls who love feminine and soft appearance. Not only creating a smooth appearance for the wearer, the spread skirt is also particularly popular thanks to the shape of the letter A suitable for all physique.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 1.75em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Time New Roman&quot;, Georgia, serif;\">CONFIDENTIAL FEMALE FEMALE</h2><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Flower motifs are always the most popular and sought-after by women in the Summer. When sewn with a soft fabric such as chiffon, cotton, a floral skirt will make girls fall in love with the feminine and gentle image.</p><div id=\"attachment_402337\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 1912px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402337\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402337\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/29/402137/chan-vay-xoe-bao-boi-cua-nang-nu-tinh-angela-baby-1.jpg\" alt=\"chân váy xòe bảo bối của nàng nữ tính angela baby dior\" 