 váy xòe dài xẻ tà áo thun đen dài tay\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1349\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402174\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 5px;\">(Ảnh: @q2han)</p></div><h2 style=\"margin: 1.75em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cambria, &quot;Time New Roman&quot;, Georgia, serif;\">WHITE LEG SKINNESS</h2><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Bohemian style \"throne\" in the summer is often synonymous with the \"coverage\" of lace. The white lace skirt brings a liberal beauty, attractive to hipster girls, and is a cool outfit for hot weather.</p><div id=\"attachment_402176\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; width: 1090px; height: auto; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 100%; padding: 5px 3px 10px; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-402176\" class=\"size-full wp-image-402176\" src=\"https://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/28/402137/chan-vay-xoe-ren-trang-ao-tank-top-yoyokulala.jpg\" alt=\"chân váy xòe ren trắng áo tank top len yoyo cao\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1350\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; height: auto; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; width: auto; display: block;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-402176\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"font-